      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im so sick of taking warfarin. it feels like i cant eat anything i want anymore because of all the vitamin k stuff and im always at the lab getting blood drawn. is there any way i can just switch to something more natural? like can i just do high dose garlic supplements and drink green smoothies every morning to keep my blood thin enough? i feel like that would be way better for my body.",
